    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon, featuring an impeccably maintained 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission delivers tactile engagement, paired with a reinforced rear subframe and a recently overhauled VANOS system to ensure mechanical longevity. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the chassis remains rigid with zero oxidation, riding on staggered Style 67 wheels wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber. Every bushing is tight, the limited-slip differential operates silently, and the compression across all six cylinders remains within factory tolerances. This is a collector-grade specimen ready for the discerning purist.",
